                            <comment id="443779" author="flei" created="Mon, 10 Feb 2025 06:59:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It is an expected result of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18032&quot; title=&quot;disable unaligned AIO&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-18032&quot;&gt;LU-18032&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="443403" author="flei" created="Thu, 6 Feb 2025 04:51:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It seems that unaligned aio is disabled deliberately. But what if the file size is not aligned? Need more investigation.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
